74
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,690
Let’s go to the lecture hall, I’ll take you there.

75
00:06:46,690 --> 00:06:49,060
Please go this way.

76
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:50,630
- Yes, I’ll escort you.
