77
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:53,050
Yes, sir.

78
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:56,060
Team Leader Jeong?

79
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:59,580
He is someone who turned down a promotion and comfortable office position,

80
00:06:59,580 --> 00:07:04,890
