84
00:07:29,700 --> 00:07:34,690
In cases like this, it’s very important to check how much battery is left in the cell phone,

85
00:07:34,690 --> 00:07:37,840
of the person you’re rescuing.

86
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:42,590
