You like it, don't you?

121
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:46,560
Wait, what is this? What’s this?

122
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:48,960
I found this!

123
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,890
Do you want this?

124
00:10:50,890 --> 00:10:52,990
Ta-Da!

125
