Why do I have a memory about Miryeong Forest?

135
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:38,710
My parents whom I even don't remember at all have no presence.

136
00:11:38,710 --> 00:11:41,980
There's just blank on the record.

137
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:45,730
Who am I supposed to ask?

138
00:11:48,070 --> 00:11:50,270
What these things are...

139
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:56,010
