199
00:19:28,820 --> 00:19:30,890
- It’s good.
- Right?

200
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:48,850
So, how long have you been in the rescue squad?

201
00:19:48,850 --> 00:19:50,380
A little over two months.

202
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:53,910
- Is it worth it?
- Yes.

203
00:20:00,890 --> 00:20:05,400
Hey. Don’t let her drink too much water.

204
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:07,130
She’ll pee a lot.

205
00:20:07,130 --> 00:20:09,430
What?

206
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:11,970
She wet her bed until she was 13 years old.

207
00:20:11,970 --> 00:20:13,530
Dad! Until I was 3.

208
00:20:13,530 --> 00:20:17,840
Don’t lie. I found her bed wet a few times until she was 13.

209
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:20,930
- How could a 13 year old—
- I wasn’t 13!

210
00:20:22,250 --> 00:20:24,730
Have a red pepper. It’s delicious.

211
00:20:26,230 --> 00:20:27,070
Not peppers.

212
00:20:27,070 --> 00:20:28,920
