243
00:22:56,560 --> 00:23:01,570
are all avoiding our calls. Like they’re colluding.

244
00:23:03,260 --> 00:23:04,980
Then we’ll go catch them.

245
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:07,350
What? Where are you going?

246
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:11,030
Shouldn’t we hunt? The slimy evaders.

247
00:23:35,530 --> 00:23:40,140
He left Naseong Development and went to work.

248
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:42,230
Yes, sir. I understand.

249
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:57,870
